title: Bob Proctor - The Success Puzzle ( Audio w/out workbook )
description:
Bob Proctor the success puzzle. I don't have the digital workbook, so please just do the best with a blank paper and do the exercises he asks. Most of the workbook he word for word speaks so...

Once again you will get no results just listening. You need to be active and take his information further..

But it is important to listen to this over and over to take your poverty mentality and change it with prosperity mentality
